item.title: CVE-2023-4590|2023-12-19T14:36:46.341Z -- frhed -- frhed
item.description: Buffer overflow vulnerability in Frhed hex editor, affecting version 1.6.0. This vulnerability could allow an attacker to execute arbitrary code via a long filename argument through the Structured Exception Handler (SEH) registers.
